text: Chari Towne (born July 26, 1960) is an American rower. She competed in the women's coxless pair event at the 1984 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1960 births Category:Living people Category:American female rowers Category:Olympic rowers of the United States Category:Rowers at the 1984 Summer Olympics Category:People from Wild Rose, Wisconsin
